item.description:
Bring your favorite photo!! It can be one that you took or from a book or web site that you have seen- just bring it along and feel free to share it with everyone in the group. Let us know why it's your favorite and what you like about it.

It's going to be a fun night!


See you Then!
Donna and Scotty
